    {
      "instruction": "<p>Crush the <strong>garlic cloves</strong> open with the side of a knife and remove the skins</p><p>Drain and rinse the <strong>red kidney beans</strong>, <strong>butter beans</strong> and <strong>black beans</strong> all together</p>",
