          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> drained beans</strong> and <strong>crushed garlic </strong>to the dish with the <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong>,<strong> cumin seeds</strong>, <strong>chopped tomatoes </strong>and <strong>chipotle paste </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Sprinkle in the <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>with 90ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[120ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>and cook for 3 hours on high – this is your <strong>slow cooker three bean chilli</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
